{"tid":1950310,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟有邊間餐廳落雨會賣炒蛋","createTime":"2020-03-30T09:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T09:35:32.000Z","uid":7192,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"466f0634006149759389600c81104b0e76d652bb","tid":1950310,"uid":7192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"問左幾間茶記都話唔賣<br />\n有啲食客聽到我話要炒蛋嚇到即刻埋單走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f10ee6200b7f6d7d3c0f1d73d10b650b159444","tid":1950310,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66427137cd4862d2f0425cb556d548159c56cc2","tid":1950310,"uid":31022,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:03:05.000Z","msg":"見你咁白癡就答下你啦<br />\n眾所週知 蛋有不同煮法 但最正宗同最原始既蛋就一定係太陽蛋 顧名思義 呢隻係要太陽下先整到既蛋 利用太陽既熱力，整熟隻蛋<br />\n<br />\n但之後陸陸續續有其他蛋煮法出現 好似炒，蒸等等<br />\n<br />\n炒蛋要用滾油，落雨會有水花 水同油因為磁通量完全唔同 兩者因為粒子性質唔同而彈開 又稱彈油 普通人一掂到輕則毀容，重則甩皮 風險極高 所以一般餐廳都唔會比員工以身犯險落雨去煮呢道菜<br />\n<br />\n有雨落炒蛋供應既餐廳只有少數 而且細佬有幸食過一次<br />\n<br />\n個種回甘真係難以忘懷..."},{"pid":"1f06d39b8b2aab24dcfc52e2885b0977aafab77a","tid":1950310,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:03:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"059725be9479fe134cea1c967cb5fd0901921dca","tid":1950310,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:03:52.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦"},{"pid":"a29621afbcbe13b60799830ca9a796343a97bdeb","tid":1950310,"uid":34256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:04:29.000Z","msg":"其實唔好笑"},{"pid":"3b77ab457d39f488eb19e7d50dff95814ef53ca6","tid":1950310,"uid":167177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:04:44.000Z","msg":"屌你去M記問啦"},{"pid":"d8a46190d733954b1ebf7a3f70e404d7a72afa09","tid":1950310,"uid":7192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b77ab457d39f488eb19e7d50dff95814